results.title: Shenzhen SHOUNUOXIN Electronics Co., Ltd. - IFA Berlin 2023
results.content: Shenzhen Shunoxin Electronics Co., Ltd. was founded in 2015, focusing on the research and development and production of intelligent charging equipment, has been leading the industry development trend and direction, is committed to the development and promotion of intelligent charging equipment industry standards.
results.raw_content:
​​​​​​​
​​​​​​​
Exhibitors
Shenzhen SHOUNUOXIN Electronics Co., Ltd.
Shenzhen Shunoxin Electronics Co., Ltd. was founded in 2015, focusing on the research and development and production of intelligent charging equipment, has been leading the industry development trend and direction, is committed to the development and promotion of intelligent charging equipment industry standards. With advanced quality testing equipment, automated machine production assembly, dust-free production workshop and other advanced production equipment, independent research and development of more than one hundred private molds, from the shell design - mold development - PCBA design - finished product production and packaging design company has an independent department to complete the speed of product development, can be customized according to customer requirements of the exclusive products, all products have a full range of safety certificates and patents! And support OEM & ODM service main production line 8, monthly production capacity of up to 3 million car chargers wireless chargers and so on.
"Excellent quality, customer satisfaction, excellence, continuous improvement" is the quality policy that Shunoxin has been adhering to for more than ten years. Quality is the foundation of Shunoxin's survival.
